<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>V6.4 技术架构 · CycleRadar Trader</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
<style>
  /* ===== Style B: Engineering Document ===== */
  /* Primary: #2D5D7C  Low-saturation Blue */
  /* S=5 L=5 B=3  (Default engineering) */

  :root {
    --bg: #F7F8FA;
    --text: #2C3E50;
    --text-muted: #5A6B7C;
    --border: #D8DEE4;

    --primary: #2D5D7C;
    --primary-light: #4A7D9C;
    --primary-pale: #E8EFF4;

    --accent-amber: #C17D2A;
    --accent-pale: #FDF3E3;

    --domain-mac: #6B7B8D;
    --domain-mac-bg: #F0F3F6;

    --domain-ecs: #2D5D7C;
    --domain-ecs-bg: #F5F8FA;

    --domain-proxy: #3D6B7A;
    --domain-proxy-bg: #F1F6F8;

    --domain-api: #5C6E7F;
    --domain-api-bg: #EEF1F4;

    --domain-db: #45606E;
    --domain-db-bg: #EDF1F4;

    --fix-color: #C17D2A;
    --fix-bg: #FEF8EE;

    --node-radius-sm: 0px;
    --node-radius-md: 4px;
    --node-radius-lg: 12px;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 28px 24px 60px;
  }

  .diagram {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .diagram-title {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .diagram-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .diagram-meta span {
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  /* ===== Three-Column Topology Grid ===== */
  .topology {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr 220px;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Column headers */
  .col-header {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ===== Left Column: Mac ===== */
  .col-left {
    padding-right: 16px;
  }

  .node-mac {
    background: var(--domain-mac-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-mac);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-lg);
    padding: 16px 14px;
  }
  .node-mac .node-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--domain-mac);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .node-mac .node-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .node-mac .component {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--domain-mac);
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
  }
  .node-mac .component:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ===== Center Column: ECS ===== */
  .col-center {
    padding: 0 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .node-ecs {
    border: 2px solid var(--domain-ecs);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .node-ecs-header {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--domain-ecs);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }

  /* Nginx node */
  .node-nginx {
    background: var(--domain-ecs-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-light);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-md);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .node-nginx .label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); }
  .node-nginx .detail { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace; }

  /* PM2 / wewe-rss node */
  .node-app {
    background: white;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-ecs);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-md);
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .node-app .label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .node-app .label .pid { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: 8px; }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .svc-block {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .svc-block .svc-name {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
  }
  .svc-block .svc-desc {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .svc-block-fix {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--fix-color);
  }

  .fix-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .fix-badge {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    background: var(--fix-bg);
    color: var(--fix-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--fix-color);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .infra-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .node-db {
    background: var(--domain-db-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-db);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .node-db .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--domain-db); }
  .node-db .detail { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 3px; font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace; }
  .node-db .tables { display: flex; gap: 6px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 4px; }
  .node-db .table { font-size: 9px; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 5px; }

  .node-cron {
    background: var(--domain-db-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-db);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .node-cron .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--domain-db); }
  .node-cron .detail { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 3px; font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace; }

  /* ===== Right Column: External ===== */
  .col-right {
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .node-proxy {
    background: var(--domain-proxy-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-proxy);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .node-proxy .node-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--domain-proxy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .node-proxy .endpoint { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace; margin-bottom: 3px; }

  .node-weread {
    background: var(--domain-api-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--domain-api);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .node-weread .node-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--domain-api); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .node-weread .detail { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ===== Connection arrows ===== */
  .arrow-box {
    position: relative;
    height: 0;
  }

  .connector-h {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: absolute;
  }

  .topology::before {
    /* SSH arrow: Mac / ECS (top edge) */
  }

  .arrow-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .flow-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 8px 0;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .flow-arrow {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .flow-arrow::after {
    content: "\25B6";
    position: absolute;
    right: -6px;
    top: -7px;
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }

  .external-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin: 14px 0 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .external-flow .pipe {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--primary-light);
  }
  .external-flow .pipe-end {
    width: 0; height: 0;
    border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-light);
    border-top: 4px solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 4px solid transparent;
  }

  .divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 28px 0;
  }

  .fix-reference {
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .fix-reference h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .fix-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .fix-table th {
    text-align: left;
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-light);
  }
  .fix-table td {
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .fix-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .fix-table .fix-id {
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fix-color);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .fix-table .file {
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .legend-swatch {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 1px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .status-badge {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: #E8F5E9;
    color: #2E7D32;
    border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    margin-left: 10px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .section-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--node-radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-card-warn {
    border-color: var(--accent-amber);
    background: var(--accent-pale);
  }

  .section-number {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .card-grid-3 {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .mini-card {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .mini-card .mc-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
  }
  .mini-card .mc-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 10.5px;
  }
  .mini-card .mc-file {
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    color: var(--domain-ecs);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .pill-ok {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    background: #E8F5E9;
    color: #2E7D32;
    border: 1px solid #A5D6A7;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 1px 7px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .pill-warn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    background: #FFF3E0;
    color: #E65100;
    border: 1px solid #FFB74D;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 1px 7px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .status-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .status-row .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    min-width: 90px;
  }

  .priority-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .priority-col {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .priority-col h4 {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .priority-col h4.p0 { color: #C62828; }
  .priority-col h4.p1 { color: var(--accent-amber); }
  .priority-col h4.p2 { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .priority-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .priority-col ul li::before {
    content: "\25B8 ";
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }

  .step-list {
    counter-reset: step;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .step-list li {
    counter-increment: step;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    background: var(--bg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .step-list li::before {
    content: counter(step) ".";
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-right: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .step-list li .step-tag {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }
  .step-list li .step-tag.tag-p0 { background: #FFCDD2; color: #C62828; }
  .step-list li .step-tag.tag-p1 { background: #FFE0B2; color: #E65100; }
  .step-list li .step-code {
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Consolas", monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--domain-ecs);
    background: white;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav', {active: 'architecture'}) %>

<div class="diagram">

  <!-- ===== TITLE BLOCK ===== -->
  <div class="diagram-title">
    周期雷达 V6.4 — 策略库 7模型 + trackerHitCard修复 + hotEvents合并 <span class="status-badge">稳定运行</span>
  </div>
  <div class="diagram-meta">
    <span>Style B / Engineering</span>
    <span>2026-06-24</span>
    <span>Dual Pipeline</span>
    <span>3-Bridge Contracts</span>
    <span>LLM策略反思</span>
    <span>launchd Auto</span>
    <span>RSS 8源 + 好运哥已激活</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== THREE-COLUMN TOPOLOGY ===== -->
  <div class="topology">

    <!-- Left col: Remote Admin -->
    <div class="col-left">
      <div class="col-header">Remote Admin</div>
      <div class="node-mac">
        <div class="node-label">Mac (Scott)</div>
        <div class="node-sub">launchd 定时任务 / SSH 运维入口</div>
        <div class="component">launchd 08:07 cron_daily.sh</div>
        <div class="component">launchd 15:00 unified.sh</div>
        <div class="component">~/交易员/ (gh-pages)</div>
        <div class="component">git push → ECS pull</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Center col: ECS -->
    <div class="col-center">
      <div class="col-header">ECS Node · 139.196.115.64</div>
      <div class="node-ecs">
        <div class="node-ecs-header">Aliyun ECS · CentOS 8 · Node v20.20.2</div>

        <!-- Nginx -->
        <div class="node-nginx">
          <div class="label">Nginx :80</div>
          <div class="detail">/m→:3100 | /trader→files | /dashboard/→301</div>
        </div>

        <!-- PM2 process matrix -->
        <div class="node-app">
          <div class="label">PM2 进程矩阵</div>
          <div class="service-grid">
            <div class="svc-block">
              <div class="svc-name">trader-admin id:7</div>
              <div class="svc-desc">:3100 / Express /m API + admin</div>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-block">
              <div class="svc-name">wewe-rss id:5</div>
              <div class="svc-desc">:4000 / RSS采集 ecosystem.config.js</div>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-block">
              <div class="svc-name">simensuji id:0</div>
              <div class="svc-desc">:3000 / 主站后端</div>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-block svc-block-fix">
              <div class="svc-name">stock_agent cron</div>
              <div class="svc-desc">15:35 Mon-Fri / Pipeline B 盘后信号</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Infra row: DB + Cron -->
        <div class="infra-row">
          <div class="node-db">
            <div class="label">3-Bridge Contracts</div>
            <div class="detail">/opt/trader/output/contracts/</div>
            <div class="tables">
              <span class="table">alpha_latest</span>
              <span class="table">event_narrative</span>
              <span class="table">upstream_signals</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail" style="font-size:9px;margin-top:2px">+ snapshots/ (90d) · daily_pnl_history</div>
          </div>
          <div class="node-cron">
            <div class="label">ECS Cron</div>
            <div class="detail">06:27 enrich_morning</div>
            <div class="detail">08:30 generate_strategy_reflection</div>
            <div class="detail">0 8,18 enrich_hot_events</div>
            <div class="detail">15:35 Mon-Fri stock_agent</div>
            <div class="detail">15:40 scanner_signal_runner</div>
            <div class="detail">15:40 rebuild_trader_views</div>
            <div class="detail">15:41 generate_backtest_html</div>
            <div class="detail">15:42 Mon-Fri snapshot_alpha</div>
            <div class="detail">15:43 Mon-Fri calc_30d_winrate</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right col: External -->
    <div class="col-right">
      <div class="col-header">External</div>
      <div class="node-proxy">
        <div class="node-label">Anthropic Claude API</div>
        <div class="endpoint">Mac daily.py → report_agent → LLM</div>
        <div class="endpoint">ECS enrich_hot_events.py → LLM</div>
        <div class="endpoint">claude-sonnet-4-6 / claude-opus-4</div>
      </div>
      <div class="node-weread">
        <div class="node-label">WeChat / WeWe RSS</div>
        <div class="detail">weread.111965.xyz proxy | Token session ~2-3h</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <hr class="divider">

  <!-- ===== SECTION: 双 Pipeline 信号交换机 ===== -->
  <div class="section-card">
    <div class="section-title">🆕 双 Pipeline 信号交换机 — upstream_signals.jsonl 唯一真相来源</div>
    <div class="status-row"><span class="pill-ok">V5.0已落地</span></div>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 6px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 10.5px; font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace; color: var(--domain-ecs); background: var(--bg); padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <span>upstream_signals.jsonl</span><span style="text-align:center">→</span><span style="text-align:center">signals.js</span><span style="text-align:center">→</span><span style="text-align:center">mobile.js</span>
      <span style="text-align:center">→</span><span style="text-align:center">/m/api/cycleradar</span><span style="text-align:center">→</span><span style="text-align:center">app.js</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);">
      <div class="mini-card">
        <div class="mc-title">Alpha <span class="pill-ok">stock_agent+report_agent</span></div>
        <div class="mc-desc">entry/target/stop/thesis</div>
